title: Beatles MP3 Menu DVD (1)
description:
This DVD contains 8 of the 16 albums by The Beatles as in the
boxed set .... I am calling this part 1 as I will be releasing part
2 in a few weeks time .... It was encoded from wav format straight
into DVD Architect and is the best quality I can get within the limitations 
of the authoring program. It is menu based with graphics for each 
album and song ....  included as each song is played are the lyrics (got 
them as close as I could) and 1 hidden song (for a bit of fun) .... there 
is no playall choice but if just left it will play on and keep looping ....
Here is a list of the Albums and Songs included:
